{"type": "article", "id": 17734, "title": "这位摄影师拍了一组时尚大片，主角是小镇上的平民", "description": "时尚穿搭 + 小镇面孔，它或许能吸引我们重新思考“时尚”。", "date": "2015-11-18T12:51:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 18913, "name": "时尚摄影"}, {"id": 18914, "name": "小镇居民"}, {"id": 18915, "name": "Merthyr Rising"}, {"id": 18916, "name": "Tom Johnson"}], "category": 19, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 68, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606161214lfgd4IWuPLY1ie8D.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t一提到时尚秀，你就会联想到终年节食的 T 台模特、拼命凹造型的明星、安娜·温图尔万年不变的蘑菇头、卡尔·拉格菲尔德宗教领袖般的号召力。但<a href=\"http://www.tom-johnson.co.uk\" target=\"_blank\">伦敦摄影师 Tom Johnson </a>却想到了更多。整个夏天，他都和设计师 Charlotte James 待在南威尔士的一个小镇里，<span> </span><span>Charlotte James 负责给小镇上的人们换装，<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/tom-johnson-merthyr-rising\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Tom 则</span></a></span><a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/tom-johnson-merthyr-rising\" target=\"_blank\">为居民们拍摄时尚照片。</a>这个小镇叫作<span> </span><span>Merthyr Tydfil ，它再平凡不过，</span>没有闪光灯，也没有 T 台，在每个人神情中，只有大写的“生活”。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161207WrECvhQfLmqOMJiB.jpg\" title=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" alt=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" data-ratio=\"1.24447514\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061612081d5IXiVKfoPpQztU.jpg\" title=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" alt=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161208fE3UF58t7aBpoqKH.jpg\" title=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" alt=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" data-ratio=\"1.26381215\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161209luhpQk9fgex8cGN2.jpg\" title=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" alt=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" data-ratio=\"0.80248619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tTom 为这系列照片起名为“冉冉升起的梅瑟蒂”（Merthyr\r\nRising），为了拍摄这些照片，他跑遍了整个小镇，从加油站到公交站，从私人庭院到劳工俱乐部。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t今年 12 月份，Tom 的照片将集结成书，届时还会有相应的展览。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161209xXRtG4nfp1Fg5Thq.jpg\" title=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" alt=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" data-ratio=\"1.27348066\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161210iEFQKX6R570dyjIn.jpg\" title=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" alt=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" data-ratio=\"1.27209945\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161211yli53bgpN1YzJcxv.jpg\" title=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" alt=\"Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Tom Johnson: Merthyr Rising</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t同样喜欢拍摄小镇居民的，还有日本现代摄影大师植田正治。植田正治 1913 年生于日本的鸟取县，1933 年在家乡成立了第一个摄影棚。直到 2000 年去世，他终生都将摄影镜头瞄准了家乡的小镇。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061612113vxT8sN14PHfaBRt.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.75625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161212ZnACYwBckxjmeMDy.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.8109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161212LEc0P7t6Bfk1Ohzd.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161213PgZIjbYJfk8pumRr.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.1359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061612139hg3nwfCXkYFlztO.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.0703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t植田正治作品\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/tom-johnson-merthyr-rising\" target=\"_blank\">itsnicethat</a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}